name: Invesco S&P 500 ESG Index ETF
longDescription: Invesco S&P 500 ESG Index ETF (the ETF) seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the S&P 500 ESG Index, or any successor thereto, on an unhedged basis, in the case of any unhedged units, or on a hedged basis, in the case of any hedged units.
